originContent: BillSplit
translatedContent: BillSplit

originContent: A modern bill splitting app. Powered by Together.ai.
translatedContent: 一个现代的账单分摊应用。由 Together.ai 提供技术支持。

originContent: ## Tech Stack
translatedContent: ## 技术栈

originContent: - Next.js 15 with App Router for modern web development
translatedContent: - 使用 App Router 的 Next.js 15 进行现代网页开发

originContent: - Together.ai for advanced LLM capabilities
translatedContent: - Together.ai 提供先进的 LLM 功能

originContent: - Helicone for LLM observability and monitoring
translatedContent: - Helicone 用于 LLM 的可观察性和监控

originContent: - Amazon S3 for secure image storage
translatedContent: - Amazon S3 用于安全的图片存储

originContent: - Vercel for seamless deployment and hosting
translatedContent: - Vercel 实现无缝部署和托管

originContent: ## How it works
translatedContent: ## 工作原理

originContent: 1. User uploads a picture of the bill
translatedContent: 1. 用户上传账单图片

originContent: 2. The app processes the PDF using Together.ai with Vision models and Json mode
translatedContent: 2. 应用使用带有视觉模型和 Json 模式的 Together.ai 处理 PDF

originContent: 3. The app let the user choose how to split items and add people names
translatedContent: 3. 应用让用户选择如何分摊项目并添加人员姓名

originContent: 4. The app displays the final summary with the split of the bill
translatedContent: 4. 应用展示账单分摊的最终汇总

originContent: ## Cloning & running
translatedContent: ## 克隆与运行

originContent: 1. Fork or clone the repo
translatedContent: 1. Fork 或克隆该仓库

originContent: 2. Create an account at https://togetherai.link for the LLM
translatedContent: 2. 在 https://togetherai.link 创建 LLM 账户

originContent: 3. Create an account at https://aws.amazon.com/ for the S3 bucket
translatedContent: 3. 在 https://aws.amazon.com/ 创建 S3 存储桶账户

originContent: 4. Create a `.env` (use the `.example.env` for reference) and replace the API keys
translatedContent: 4. 创建 `.env` 文件（参考 `.example.env`）并替换 API 密钥

originContent: 5. Run `pnpm install` and `pnpm run dev` to install dependencies and run locally
translatedContent: 5. 运行 `pnpm install` 和 `pnpm run dev` 以安装依赖并本地运行
